source1 keyGenerate(output(Member_Enrollment_ID as long),
	startAt: 1L) ~> SurrogateKey1
source2 derive(Member_Key = (MEMBER_ID+SSN),
		DOB = coalesce(toDate(DOB,'MM/dd/yyyy'),toDate(DOB,'dd-MM-yyyy'),toDate(DOB,'yyyy/MM/dd'),toDate(DOB,'dd/MM/yyyy'),toDate(DOB,'MMddyyyy'),toDate(DOB,'yyyyddMM'),toDate(DOB,'MMddyyyy'),toDate(DOB,'yyyyMMdd')),
		Deceased_Date = toDate(Deceased_Date)) ~> DerivedColumn1
DerivedColumn1, SurrogateKey1 lookup(source2@MEMBER_ID == source1@MEMBER_ID,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Lookup1
